@SIEG.SrDevChallenge.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5298
@ApiKey = dev-api-key-123456789

### GET Documentos Fiscais (Lista Paginada)
GET {{SIEG.SrDevChallenge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documentos-fiscais?DataInicio=2024-01-01&DataFim=2024-12-31&DocumentoEmissor=12345678000199&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### GET Documento Fiscal por ID  
GET {{SIEG.SrDevChallenge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documentos-fiscais/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### POST Upload de XML (Documento Fiscal)
POST {{SIEG.SrDevChallenge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documentos-fiscais
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="documento.xml"
Content-Type: application/xml

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<nfeProc>
  <!-- Conteúdo do XML aqui -->
</nfeProc>
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### DELETE Documento Fiscal
DELETE {{SIEG.SrDevChallenge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documentos-fiscais/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Exemplo com API Key inválida (deve retornar 401)
GET {{SIEG.SrDevChallenge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documentos-fiscais?DataInicio=2024-01-01&DataFim=2024-12-31&DocumentoEmissor=12345678000199
X-API-Key: chave-invalida
Accept: application/json

### Exemplo sem API Key (deve retornar 401)
GET {{SIEG.SrDevChallenge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documentos-fiscais?DataInicio=2024-01-01&DataFim=2024-12-31&DocumentoEmissor=12345678000199
Accept: application/json

###
